Static Function fChamaFunc 
****************************

Local I

/** Atribuicao de parametros fixos **/

aData := {_dData1,_dData2,_dData3,_dData4,_dData5}

/** Alteracao de parametros **/
For i := 1 To Len(aParam)    
 	FMudaParam(aData[i],aParam[i])                                          
Next                                                                       
Close(Dlg01)
Return

